in development enable adb and debug as root
connect as File Transfer

adb -d reboot sideload
this will get into recovery with sideload

adb -d sideload Downloads/lineage-17.1-20210518-nightly-lavender-signed.zip
if it will get adb: sideload connection failed: insufficient permissions for device

then
adb kill-server
sudo adb start-server
detech the device and plug it again
adb -d sideload Downloads/lineage-17.1-20210518-nightly-lavender-signed.zip

